{"id":437787,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/05/【麻辣总局】-微美术馆：48小时征集艺术作品《打/","date":"2016-05-13T22:36:55Z","modified":"2016-05-13T22:59:36Z","title":"【麻辣总局】微美术馆：48小时征集艺术作品《打飞机》 ","content":"<p><span id=\"post-date\" class=\"rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text\">2016-05-13</span> <span class=\"rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text\">一起来吧</span></p>\n<div class=\"rich_media_meta_list\"></div>\n<div id=\"js_content\" class=\"rich_media_content \">\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437788\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/0.gif\" alt=\"0\" width=\"467\" height=\"700\" /></p>\n<p>注：征集海报为陈学刚作品，作于2016年5月</p>\n<fieldset>你也许打过飞机，但是你绝没有辣么明目张胆的打过飞机。打飞机不可怕，可怕的是你不敢让人知道你打了飞机；打飞机不可耻，可耻的是你以为打飞机很可耻。飞机就在那，你打或不打，它就在那里，你动或不动，它就在那里。。。</p>\n<p>打飞机，你需要换个姿势了！</p>\n<p>值得注意的是，这次打飞机只是一次艺术交流活动，不会有生命危险~</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437789\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/1.gif\" alt=\"1\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" /></fieldset>\n<fieldset>征集方：微美术馆</p>\n<p>策展人：梁克刚、信王军、刘石石石</p>\n<p>征集：</p>\n<p>1，必须为打飞机相关主题范围作品</p>\n<p>2，作品种类不限，可以为GIF、海报、摄影、油画、设计、行为艺术等等，（需注明作品名称、大小、材料、时间、作者等信息，图片格式为jpg、gif）</p>\n<p>3，以上信息以压缩包的形式提交至邮箱<strong>iaptuya@163.com</strong></p>\n<p>4，征集时间：2016.5.13日下午5点发布——5.15日下午5点截止</p>\n<p>5，展示：5.16日在微美术馆公众号上开始长期展示<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437790\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/3.gif\" alt=\"3\" width=\"500\" height=\"189\" /></fieldset>\n<fieldset><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437803\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/653.jpg\" alt=\"653\" width=\"438\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/653.jpg 438w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/653-219x300.jpg 219w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 438px) 100vw, 438px\" /></p>\n<p class=\"pictext\">　　1970年代中国出版的步枪打飞机教程插图。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437802\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/652.jpg\" alt=\"652\" width=\"450\" height=\"616\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/652.jpg 450w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/652-219x300.jpg 219w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<p class=\"pictext\">　　1970年代中国出版的步枪打飞机教程插图。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437801\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/651.jpg\" alt=\"651\" width=\"584\" height=\"428\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/651.jpg 584w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/651-300x220.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437800\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/650.jpg\" alt=\"650\" width=\"490\" height=\"485\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/650.jpg 490w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/650-300x297.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/650-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/650-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 490px) 100vw, 490px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437799\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/649.jpg\" alt=\"649\" width=\"584\" height=\"403\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/649.jpg 584w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/649-300x207.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437798\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/648.jpg\" alt=\"648\" width=\"584\" height=\"409\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/648.jpg 584w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/648-300x210.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 584px) 100vw, 584px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437797\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/647.jpg\" alt=\"647\" width=\"442\" height=\"586\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/647.jpg 442w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/647-226x300.jpg 226w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 442px) 100vw, 442px\" /></p>\n<p class=\"pictext\">　《打飞机英雄集》。（来源：资料图）</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437796\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/646.jpg\" alt=\"646\" width=\"422\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/646.jpg 422w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/646-253x300.jpg 253w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 422px) 100vw, 422px\" /></p>\n<p class=\"pictext\">　　1965年出版《怎样打飞机》（来源：资料图）</p>\n<p><wbr /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437795\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/645.jpg\" alt=\"645\" width=\"604\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/645.jpg 604w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/645-300x192.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 604px) 100vw, 604px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437794\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/644.jpg\" alt=\"644\" width=\"482\" height=\"497\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/644.jpg 482w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/644-291x300.jpg 291w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 482px) 100vw, 482px\" /> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437793\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/643.jpg\" alt=\"643\" width=\"640\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/643.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/643-300x246.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></fieldset>\n<p>扫描下面二维码</p>\n<p><strong>告诉我，你要怎样打飞机？</strong></p>\n<p>策展人梁克刚微信</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437792\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/641.jpg\" alt=\"641\" width=\"250\" height=\"248\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/641.jpg 250w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/641-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/641-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/641-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" /></p>\n<p>扫描关注微美术馆</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-437791\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/640-4.jpg\" alt=\"640\" width=\"430\" height=\"430\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/640-4.jpg 430w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/640-4-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/640-4-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/640-4-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/05/640-4-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 100vw, 430px\" /></p>\n<p>前方高能支持</p>\n</div>\n","author":973,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,13789],"tags":[23261,31012]}